WEBVTT

00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:25.079
Lu Chengwen

00:01:26.959 --> 00:01:29.079
I actually really regret it.

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:31.359
Not cherishing your feelings for me before.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:34.920
Can't we

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:36.480
just start over?

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:43.719
No.

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:45.120
Why?

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:47.920
Xu Xuejiao isn't your girlfriend at all.

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:49.680
And you don't have anyone you like.

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:50.480
Right?

00:01:51.879 --> 00:01:53.359
When did I blow my cover?

00:01:55.120 --> 00:01:55.920
No.

00:01:56.359 --> 00:01:57.719
I do have someone I like.

00:01:57.760 --> 00:01:58.599
I really do.

00:01:59.319 --> 00:02:00.280
It's that...

00:02:00.799 --> 00:02:01.599
Who is it?

00:02:03.480 --> 00:02:04.319
It's...

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:10.159
Young Master Lu got bailed out already?

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:15.280
It's my secretary, Jiang Shihan.

00:02:15.919 --> 00:02:17.520
If you don't believe me, ask Little Xuejiao.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:19.479
Shihan's mother is seriously ill.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:21.919
I humbly begged Xuejiao for a long time,

00:02:21.919 --> 00:02:23.560
before she agreed to help save her mother.

00:02:23.719 --> 00:02:24.680
Thank you, Xuejiao.

00:02:25.759 --> 00:02:26.800
What are you thanking me for?

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:28.319
You traded your pharma factory's

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:30.560
18 billion in shares for this.

00:02:31.759 --> 00:02:32.560
Right.

00:02:32.759 --> 00:02:34.199
He used the pharma factory's shares?

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:35.159
Yeah.

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:36.879
I like her.

00:02:36.919 --> 00:02:37.800
I love her.

00:02:37.919 --> 00:02:39.360
I've fallen for her.

00:02:39.479 --> 00:02:42.199
I want to bring her home to be my wife.

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:44.759
Young Master Lu picking up girls

00:02:44.759 --> 00:02:47.199
is certainly generous.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:50.599
That's just the kind of thing I do.

00:02:56.520 --> 00:02:57.319
Scumbag.

00:02:57.479 --> 00:02:58.599
He actually, for a secretary...

00:02:58.599 --> 00:02:59.919
spent 18 billion.

00:03:00.159 --> 00:03:01.199
Believe me now?

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:02.599
Get lost.

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:04.120
Let's go.

00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:04.599
Young Master Lu.

00:03:04.599 --> 00:03:06.120
Let's go sign the contract right now.

00:03:06.479 --> 00:03:07.319
Let's go.

00:03:08.120 --> 00:03:08.719
Let's go.

00:03:08.719 --> 00:03:09.479
Bye-bye.

00:03:30.719 --> 00:03:31.960
You didn't even look closely.

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.280
Aren't you afraid I'll scam you?

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:34.520
If you wanted to scam me,

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:36.120
how could I possibly defend against it?

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:37.719
He actually didn't back out.

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:39.080
He really signed it.

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:40.240
Does he even know

00:03:40.240 --> 00:03:41.280
what he's doing?

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:43.319
This is 18 billion!

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.159
It can't be

00:03:44.159 --> 00:03:46.159
that he really has feelings for Jiang Shihan, right?

00:03:46.199 --> 00:03:47.080
You...

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:48.360
Why did you sign this contract?

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:51.680
Isn't this what you asked for?

00:03:51.879 --> 00:03:53.120
Since I agreed to it,

00:03:53.159 --> 00:03:54.199
I naturally have to do it.

00:03:54.599 --> 00:03:55.840
Going back on my word

00:03:55.840 --> 00:03:56.599
is not an option.

00:03:58.960 --> 00:03:59.759
Lu Chengwen,

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.280
what exactly are you trying to do?

00:04:01.960 --> 00:04:03.120
What do you mean?

00:04:03.719 --> 00:04:05.520
You just made 18 billion!

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:06.960
If you let me make that much money,

00:04:06.960 --> 00:04:08.960
I'd probably kneel down and bow to you.

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:10.199
Are you crazy?

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:13.879
Just take the shares and leave.

00:04:14.360 --> 00:04:15.560
Be a good girl and follow your plot.

00:04:15.719 --> 00:04:17.079
Hurry up and go find Gu Zhantian.

00:04:17.279 --> 00:04:18.519
Let's just stay out of each other's way.

00:04:18.519 --> 00:04:19.279
Isn't that good?

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:23.800
So,

00:04:24.399 --> 00:04:26.120
he did this just to get rid of me?

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:29.120
Does he really hate me that much?

00:04:29.920 --> 00:04:31.319
Am I really that annoying to you?

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:32.720
Do you want to drive me away that badly?

00:04:34.399 --> 00:04:35.279
Little Xuejiao...

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:37.120
Lu Chengwen,

00:04:37.279 --> 00:04:38.279
I'm not you.

00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:40.399
I won't trade a patient's life for profit.

00:04:40.519 --> 00:04:41.279
These shares,

00:04:41.279 --> 00:04:42.399
you can keep them for yourself.

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.800
He's looking at me so seriously.

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:50.959
Could it be...

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:52.240
Maybe...

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:54.800
they can hear what I'm thinking?

00:05:02.120 --> 00:05:03.560
Xu Xuejiao, oh, Xu Xuejiao.

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:05.959
I originally wanted to let the Xu family off the hook.

00:05:06.199 --> 00:05:08.279
But since you're rushing to your death,

00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:12.279
Lu Chengwen is going to attack the Xu family?

00:05:19.959 --> 00:05:20.879
Little Xuejiao,

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:22.399
since that's the case,

00:05:22.959 --> 00:05:24.720
I'll just keep the shares then.

00:05:25.199 --> 00:05:26.519
And as for you,

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:30.519
you should stay too.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.120
How did Lu Chengwen turn back into

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:41.480
this jerk again?

00:05:42.279 --> 00:05:44.120
Which one is the real him?

00:05:44.680 --> 00:05:45.480
No, no.

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:47.319
His pulse is racing.

00:05:47.399 --> 00:05:48.279
He's very nervous.

00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:49.879
He...

00:05:49.879 --> 00:05:51.160
is faking it.

00:05:55.319 --> 00:05:56.399
Brother Chengwen,

00:05:56.879 --> 00:05:57.920
since when

00:05:57.920 --> 00:05:59.079
did you figure out

00:05:59.079 --> 00:06:00.920
that I can hear your inner thoughts?

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:05.680
You...

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:10.519
Brother Chengwen,

00:06:11.079 --> 00:06:11.839
since

00:06:11.839 --> 00:06:13.680
you want me to stay,

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:14.879
then

00:06:14.879 --> 00:06:16.680
starting from today,

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.959
I'll be sticking to you all the time.

00:06:24.879 --> 00:06:26.079
Don't do anything crazy!

00:06:28.279 --> 00:06:29.399
Brother Chengwen,

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:30.879
what are you talking about?

00:06:40.399 --> 00:06:41.680
Brother Chengwen,

00:06:42.120 --> 00:06:43.279
I just want to

00:06:43.279 --> 00:06:45.160
get to know you better.

00:07:03.680 --> 00:07:05.759
This Xu Xuejiao is way too bizarre.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:08.000
How did she see right through me?

00:07:16.360 --> 00:07:16.759
Dad.

00:07:16.759 --> 00:07:17.560
You little brat.

00:07:18.600 --> 00:07:20.319
Hurry up and go to the Chen family's place.

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:22.120
The old master says he wants to see you.

00:07:22.199 --> 00:07:23.079
If you're late,

00:07:23.079 --> 00:07:24.360
I'll break your legs.

00:07:26.600 --> 00:07:27.800
I got it, Dad.

00:07:28.920 --> 00:07:29.720
Old Master.

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:30.680
This medicine...

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:31.920
...works pretty well, right?

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:32.800
Yeah.

00:07:37.720 --> 00:07:39.040
Thank you, Old Master, for not...

00:07:39.040 --> 00:07:40.120
...stooping to my level before.

00:07:40.519 --> 00:07:41.199
The business world...

00:07:41.199 --> 00:07:42.279
...is like a battlefield.

00:07:43.000 --> 00:07:45.079
I was simply outskilled.

00:07:45.120 --> 00:07:46.519
What's there to hold a grudge over?

00:07:47.480 --> 00:07:49.079
That's why they say you have a broad vision.

00:07:49.079 --> 00:07:49.879
Right?

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:51.399
Brother Chengwen is here!

00:07:51.920 --> 00:07:53.519
Grandpa, have some fruit after your medicine.

00:07:53.519 --> 00:07:54.120
Okay.

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:54.920
Haha.

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:18.480
Xiaoqi.

00:08:31.920 --> 00:08:32.759
You smelly loser.

00:08:32.799 --> 00:08:33.759
Peeking at Xiaoqi again.

00:08:33.759 --> 00:08:34.559
Are you worthy?

00:08:34.679 --> 00:08:36.320
Take a look at yourself in the mirror.

00:08:38.919 --> 00:08:39.679
How could she look...

00:08:39.679 --> 00:08:41.080
...like my first love goddess?

00:08:42.799 --> 00:08:43.600
You brat.

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:45.519
Seize the opportunity.

00:08:46.679 --> 00:08:47.679
What's going on?

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:50.480
Mengyun's figure and looks...

00:08:50.480 --> 00:08:51.679
...and inner beauty...

00:08:51.919 --> 00:08:54.000
What man wouldn't want to marry her?

00:08:54.279 --> 00:08:55.120
You brat.

00:08:55.279 --> 00:08:56.559
Stop pretending.

00:08:56.919 --> 00:08:58.080
Hahaha.

00:08:59.519 --> 00:09:00.320
Mengyun.

00:09:02.200 --> 00:09:03.000
Chen Mengyun.

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:06.279
Chen Mengyun.

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:07.679
One of the four main female leads.

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:09.519
Jiao Shiheng lusted after her beauty.

00:09:09.679 --> 00:09:11.000
He drugged her to take advantage of her.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:13.120
Luckily, Gu Zhantian arrived in time.

00:09:13.399 --> 00:09:14.879
So Chen Mengyun was saved from disaster.

00:09:15.720 --> 00:09:17.919
I was wondering why the fourth female lead hadn't appeared.

00:09:18.279 --> 00:09:20.519
Turns out she's not on my villain storyline.

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:22.360
That means...

00:09:28.720 --> 00:09:30.519
Chen Mengyun has nothing to do with me.

00:09:30.679 --> 00:09:31.879
Then I can rest easy.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.080
No need to run away.

00:09:33.679 --> 00:09:34.480
Strange.

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:37.480
I seem to be able to hear Lu Chengwen's inner thoughts.

00:09:37.799 --> 00:09:39.399
But why can't I understand them?

00:09:40.080 --> 00:09:41.000
The fruit is ready.

00:09:41.399 --> 00:09:42.720
Come have some fruit.

00:09:42.919 --> 00:09:44.120
I called him over for you.

00:09:44.679 --> 00:09:46.120
Grandpa is the best, right?

00:09:46.360 --> 00:09:47.159
Grandpa!

00:09:47.279 --> 00:09:48.279
What are you talking about?

00:09:48.919 --> 00:09:50.759
What do you mean called him over?

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:53.480
This fruit was just airlifted from abroad.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:54.519
Try some.

00:09:58.559 --> 00:09:59.360
Thanks.

00:10:02.919 --> 00:10:04.559
If all of this is true...

00:10:04.960 --> 00:10:06.120
That would be so great.

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:07.879
He seems to

00:10:07.879 --> 00:10:09.320
really like me.

00:10:09.720 --> 00:10:10.679
Tomorrow night,

00:10:11.159 --> 00:10:12.919
I've booked the entire Haicheng Cinema.

00:10:13.159 --> 00:10:14.559
Both of you are going.

00:10:16.679 --> 00:10:17.840
Dating a female lead from

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:19.279
another villain's storyline

00:10:19.559 --> 00:10:20.960
shouldn't affect the plot, right?

00:10:21.399 --> 00:10:23.120
When Gu Zhantian saves her later,

00:10:23.519 --> 00:10:24.600
she'll still be his.

00:10:24.879 --> 00:10:25.679
Mengyun,

00:10:25.919 --> 00:10:26.919
Grandpa is hoping you

00:10:26.919 --> 00:10:28.000
get married soon

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:28.879
and have a baby.

00:10:29.120 --> 00:10:30.399
In a person's whole life,

00:10:30.480 --> 00:10:31.799
the only thing you truly care about

00:10:31.799 --> 00:10:32.480
in the end

00:10:32.480 --> 00:10:33.720
is family.

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:34.799
Grandpa,

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:37.360
I still need to find someone I like.

00:10:38.080 --> 00:10:38.879
That's right.

00:10:38.879 --> 00:10:40.960
You get together with someone you like,

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:42.120
and then

00:10:42.120 --> 00:10:43.799
get married and have a baby.

00:10:43.960 --> 00:10:45.279
Then a family of three...

00:10:45.960 --> 00:10:47.080
How happy would that be?

00:10:47.120 --> 00:10:47.919
Right?

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:48.960
Alright then,

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.320
you two keep chatting.

00:10:50.679 --> 00:10:52.320
I'll head back to my room first.

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:57.799
Thank you.

00:11:03.279 --> 00:11:04.080
Hello?

00:11:05.879 --> 00:11:06.679
Mr. Jiao?

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:08.399
Mr. Jiao.

00:11:08.679 --> 00:11:09.480
Jiao Shiheng.

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:11.480
Looks like this kid's time is up.

00:11:11.480 --> 00:11:12.240
Tomorrow night?

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:13.480
Tomorrow night might not work.

00:11:14.120 --> 00:11:15.320
I have plans tomorrow night.

00:11:15.919 --> 00:11:16.679
What?

00:11:16.919 --> 00:11:17.679
Tomorrow night?

00:11:17.759 --> 00:11:19.320
I've affected the main plot!

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:20.960
Darn it!